uk.ac.man.entitytagger.generate
Class DictionaryEntry

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.man.entitytagger.generate.DictionaryEntry

public class DictionaryEntry
extends java.lang.Object

A class representing a dictionary entry of some object, consisting of a number of regular expression synonyms and an id. This could for instance be a species with id 9606 and synonyms "human" and "man"

Author:
Martin
